    <item>
      <title>How to remember ssh keys on mac os</title>
      <link>https://yantonov.com/post/2019-12-15-how-to-remember-ssh-keys-on-mac-os/</link>
      <guid>https://yantonov.com/post/2019-12-15-how-to-remember-ssh-keys-on-mac-os/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2019 19:04:37 +0500</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Got tired to enter ssh passphrases on mac os and want to know how easily force ssh-agent to remember ssh keys?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add this snippet to ~/.ssh/config file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Host *
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;     AddKeysToAgent yes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;     UseKeychain yes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/technotes/tn2449/_index.html&#34;&gt;Source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
